T=\sum_{n=0}^\infty (n+1)T_1 [e^{-n\lambda_1T_1} - e^{-(n+1)\lambda_1T_1}]
=\sum_{n=0}^\infty (n+1)T_1 e^{-n\lambda_1T_1} - \sum_{n=0}^\infty (n+1)T_1 e^{-(n+1)\lambda_1T_1}
=\sum_{n=0}^\infty (n+1)T_1 e^{-n\lambda_1T_1} - \sum_{n=1}^\infty nT_1 e^{-n\lambda_1T_1}
=T_1 + \sum_{n=1}^\infty T_1 e^{-n\lambda_1T_1}
=\sum_{n=0}^\infty T_1 e^{-n\lambda_1T_1}
